    <p>Synthetic opioids like fentanyl have made street drugs increasingly deadly. Even drugs not intended to contain opioids (cocaine, pressed pills, etc.) may be contaminated. Always use test strips, carry naloxone, and never use alone. The margin for error is essentially zero.</p>
